%%{init: {'flowchart': {'curve': 'stepAfter', 'nodeSpacing': 30, 'rankSpacing': 40}}}%%
flowchart LR
    classDef startEnd fill:#000,stroke:#000,color:#fff
    classDef decision fill:#FFD700,stroke:#B8860B,color:#000
    classDef activity fill:#fff,stroke:#000,color:#000

    Start((Start)):::startEnd

    Start --> UserValid[User<br/>Validation]:::activity
    UserValid --> AuthCheck{Login<br/>Failed}:::decision
    AuthCheck -->|Yes| ForgotPW[Forgot Password]:::activity
    ForgotPW --> ResetPW[Reset<br/>Password]:::activity
    ResetPW --> UserValid
    AuthCheck -->|No| AdminDash[Display Admin<br/>Dashboard]:::activity
    AdminDash --> D1{Action?}:::decision

    D1 -->|Logout| Logout[Log out]:::activity
    Logout --> EndL((End)):::startEnd

    D1 -->|User Mgmt| SearchUsers[Search Users<br/>by Email / Name]:::activity
    SearchUsers --> UserAction{User<br/>action?}:::decision
    UserAction -->|Suspend| Suspend[Suspend User<br/>Account]:::activity
    Suspend --> AutoLog1[Auto-Log<br/>Admin Action]:::activity
    AutoLog1 --> MA{More<br/>Actions<br/>to do}:::decision
    UserAction -->|Unsuspend| Unsuspend[Unsuspend User<br/>Account]:::activity
    Unsuspend --> AutoLog2[Auto-Log<br/>Admin Action]:::activity
    AutoLog2 --> MA
    UserAction -->|Reset Password| ResetUserPW[Reset User<br/>Password]:::activity
    ResetUserPW --> AutoLog3[Auto-Log<br/>Admin Action]:::activity
    AutoLog3 --> MA
    UserAction -->|Modify Tier| ModifyTier[Modify User<br/>Subscription Tier]:::activity
    ModifyTier --> AutoLog4[Auto-Log<br/>Admin Action]:::activity
    AutoLog4 --> MA

    D1 -->|Audit Logs| ViewAudit[View Immutable<br/>Audit Logs]:::activity
    ViewAudit --> ReviewLogs[Review Flagged<br/>Actions]:::activity
    ReviewLogs --> MB{More<br/>Actions<br/>to do}:::decision

    D1 -->|System Health| CheckHealth[Monitor System<br/>Health]:::activity
    CheckHealth --> ViewServices[View DB / Redis /<br/>Celery Status &<br/>CPU / Memory]:::activity
    ViewServices --> MB

    D1 -->|Configure Demo| DemoAction{Demo<br/>action?}:::decision
    DemoAction -->|Start| StartDemo[Start Demo<br/>Simulation]:::activity
    StartDemo --> FanoutDemo[Fanout Demo Alerts<br/>to All Tier DBs]:::activity
    FanoutDemo --> MC{More<br/>Actions<br/>to do}:::decision
    DemoAction -->|Clear| ClearDemo[Clear All<br/>Demo Data]:::activity
    ClearDemo --> MC

    MA -->|Yes| AdminDash
    MB -->|Yes| AdminDash
    MC -->|Yes| AdminDash

    MA -->|No| E1((End)):::startEnd
    MB -->|No| E2((End)):::startEnd
    MC -->|No| E3((End)):::startEnd
